Ventral and lateral views of the aedeagus of the new species and ventral view of median lobe: 15 and 16) Aedeagus of 
<taxonomicName box="[346,460,1915,1938]" class="Insecta" family="Lucanidae" genus="Leptinopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="asketus">
<emphasis box="[346,460,1915,1938]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="39">L. asketus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 18 and 19) Aedeagus of 
<taxonomicName box="[755,885,1915,1938]" class="Insecta" family="Lucanidae" genus="Leptinopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="assimilis">
<emphasis box="[755,885,1915,1938]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="39">L. assimilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. (Figs. 15 and 18, setae and apex of internal sac omitted). Scale bar = 1 mm. 17) Ventral view of median lobe of 
<taxonomicName box="[880,993,1952,1975]" class="Insecta" family="Lucanidae" genus="Leptinopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="asketus">
<emphasis box="[880,993,1952,1975]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="39">L. asketus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 20) Ventral view of median lobe of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Lucanidae" genus="Leptinopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="assimilis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="39">L. assimilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Scale bar = 0.5 mm.
